d a timeout to set up a inbounds play at midcourt.But Westbook, going for the win, missed a 3-pointer from the left wing instead of driving to the hole and the Hornets and P.J. Washington secured the rebound. Washington added a free throw with 0.2 left for the final margin.TIP INSLakers: Were outscored 58-38 in the paint.Hornets: Mason Plumlee had a season-high 17 rebounds. Plumlee was called for defensive 3 seconds twice in the same possession in the second half. ... Cody Martin had a remarkable block on Westbrook, chasing him down the lane and beating the shot off the glass from behind.UP NEXTLakers: At Atlanta on Sunday.Hornets: Host Los Angeles Clippers on Sunday.___More AP NBA: https://apnews.com/hub/NBA and https://twitter.com/AP_Sports